#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Kamoso Handbook"
msgstr "Kamoso 手册"

#. Tag: personname
#: index.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<firstname>This documentation was converted from the KDE UserBase <ulink url="
"\"http://userbase.kde.org/Kamoso\">Kamoso</ulink> page and updated by the "
"&kde; documentation team.</firstname> <surname></surname>"
msgstr ""
"<firstname>本文档转化自 KDE UserBase <ulink url=\" http://userbase.kde.org/"
"Kamoso\">Kamoso</ulink> 页面并由 &kde; 文档组维护。</firstname> <surname></"
"surname>"

#. Tag: trans_comment
#: index.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "ROLES_OF_TRANSLATORS"
msgstr "<author><firstname>Yunhe</firstname> <surname>Guo</surname></author>"

#. Tag: date
#: index.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "2016-08-24"
msgstr "2016-08-24"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kamoso; 3.2"
msgstr "&kamoso; 3.2"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "Take a shot"
msgstr "拍摄照片"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kamoso; gives you an opportunity to make photos from your webcam and upload "
"them to Internet"
msgstr "&kamoso; 使您能够用摄像头拍摄照片，并且上传到互联网"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "Record video"
msgstr "录制视频"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kamoso; allows to record videos from your webcam and upload them to the "
"Internet"
msgstr "&kamoso; 使您可以用摄像头录制视频并且上传到互联网上"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "User Guide"
msgstr "用户指南"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Welcome to &kamoso;!"
msgstr "欢迎使用 &kamoso; ！"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kamoso; is a great program to use your webcam to take pictures or make "
"videos. This guide will help you to use &kamoso; once you have installed it."
msgstr ""
"&kamoso; 是一个优秀的用摄像头来拍摄照片与视频的程序。本向导指导您在安装 "
"&kamoso; 之后如何使用它。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "快速入门"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On launching &kamoso;, it displays this window with buttons at the bottom:"
msgstr "启动 &kamoso;，后，它会显示底端包含这些按钮的窗口："

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to <guibutton>Shoot</guibutton> mode to take one picture"
msgstr "切换到 <guibutton>照相</guibutton> 模式来拍摄一张相片。"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch to <guibutton>Burst</guibutton> mode and take continuously pictures "
"until you stop by clicking the middle button again"
msgstr ""
"切换到 <guibutton>连拍</guibutton> 模式，您可以连续不断地拍摄相片，直到您再次"
"点击中央的按钮来停止。"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to <guibutton>Record</guibutton> mode to record a video"
msgstr "切换到 <guibutton>录像</guibutton> 模式来录制视频"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start or stop taking pictures or recording a video"
msgstr "开始或停止拍摄照片或录制视频"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show gallery"
msgstr "显示相册"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show settings"
msgstr "显示设置"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pictures and videos are numbered consecutively and saved automatically in "
"the <guilabel>Captures directory</guilabel> defined in the settings."
msgstr ""
"照片和视频会被顺序编号，保存在设置中的 <guilabel>拍摄内容目录</guilabel>。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing Captures"
msgstr "管理拍摄内容"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view and manage your captured pictures or videos click the "
"<guibutton>Show gallery</guibutton> button. In the context menu for each "
"entry in the gallery you find actions to manage them:"
msgstr ""
"点击 <guibutton>显示相册</guibutton> 按钮可以查看并管理您拍摄的照片及视频。在"
"相册中项目的右键菜单中，您可以找到用于管理它们的操作："

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guimenuitem>Open</guimenuitem> to view your captures in the associated "
"application."
msgstr ""
"用 <guimenuitem>打开</guimenuitem> 操作来使用对应的程序查看您的拍摄内容。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to delete pictures and videos open the captures folder in the "
"filemanager."
msgstr "如果您想要删除照片或视频，使用文件管理器打开录制文件夹。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next actions allow you to upload captures to the Internet or send them "
"to a contact or device."
msgstr "接下来的操作使您可以将拍摄内容上传到互联网或者发给联系人或设备。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guimenuitem>Save as</guimenuitem> to copy the complete content of the "
"gallery to a new folder."
msgstr ""
"使用 <guimenuitem>另存为</guimenuitem> 可将相册的完整内容保存到一个新目录。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizing"
msgstr "自定义"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Show settings</guibutton> button to open the settings "
"panel. Click the button again to hide the settings panel."
msgstr ""
"点击 <guibutton>显示设置</guibutton> 按钮来打开设置面板。再次点击可隐藏设置面"
"板。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to change the folder where &kamoso; saves pictures and videos, "
"change the <guilabel>Captures directory</guilabel> at the top."
msgstr ""
"如果您想要更改 &kamoso; 保存照片和视频的目录，更改顶端的 <guilabel>拍摄内容目"
"录</guilabel>。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable <guibutton>Use flash</guibutton> to highlight the window before "
"taking photos."
msgstr "启用 <guibutton>使用高亮</guibutton> 可在拍摄照片前使窗口高亮。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the sliders you can modify camera settings like brightness, hue, "
"contrast, saturation and gamma."
msgstr ""
"利用这些滑块，您可以修改相机设置，例如亮度，色调，对比度，饱和度和伽马。"

